Package: snippetsaddin
Type: Package
Title: RStudio add-in to add some code snippets, or help with code editing
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person( "Juraj", "Sofranko", role = c("aut", "cre")
                 , email="replace_with_my_first_name.replace_with_my_last_name@gmail.com")
Description: This package is an add-in to RStudio for Windows. In the current
    release it contains pipe insertion and its surroundings reformatting;
    slashes reversing; and copying values of variables under the cursor into
    clipboard.
